      • writeReport

        void writeReport(wt.change2.WTChangeReview changeReview,
                 NmCommandBean cb)
          throws WTException,
                 DocumentException
        Write the report. This method calls each of write methods. Each method writes the corresponding section of the report. Order of sections:

        Header
        Attributes
        Attachments
        Annotations
        Affected Objects
        Process Objects
        Reference Objects
        Action Items
